{"tid":944952,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得意義衣啲片好高質","createTime":"2018-12-17T13:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T06:04:21.000Z","uid":212825,"like":27,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2a5179f687224ba947f64a601172eb382eccdc","tid":944952,"uid":212825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"佢哋有時會講番唔同牌子/衫的歷史同埋背景，仲會教埋觀眾點襯（仲要大部分都襯得幾好睇），部分街訪都ok好笑（雖然有啲笑位係夾硬嚟）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢哋嘅片仲要幾多元化，軍裝又有，工裝又有，復古風又有，唔會話淨係死跟一種style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有襯衫唔一定睇brand，有時佢哋穿u記、GU、TB啲衫都襯得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n22e喺香港呢個着衫風格保守的地方，簡直係清泉，好想佢哋快啲再出片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2320e06432f9cfd0e6c06516130114ca8cbfaaa","tid":944952,"uid":53306,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"Goggle 都有😁"},{"pid":"c312d80cc70519ccc4c8be254b0492a9db88bd0a","tid":944952,"uid":14739,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"講句古著有故事 已經大讚 <br />\n內容空泛到仆街<br />\n又hard sell 自己個垃圾袋仔<br />\n柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪又係跟風出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c046dd1cf923d370318cd1dc53c3d8a711bdd132","tid":944952,"uid":80797,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"打手？"},{"pid":"7aba8ea271be0369504fe73351d9cb22362b54a7","tid":944952,"uid":27370,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"喺連登度講衣著係禁忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f414d85f1e43de4f71d1bea995d832c0178a1d51","tid":944952,"uid":109598,"